Let $Key = 0

** Set Up the Subroutines

Call o2oSupport
Call QuickKeys Setup
Call SpeedSwitching Setup
Call DropKick Setup
** Call PhastPhunctions Setup
Call o2o Setup 0 ** use TrainPlayer loads
** Call o2o Setup 1 ** use JMRI loads
** Call TurnTable Setup 2
** Language choices are: en, de, fr, sp
Call SetLanguage en
Call NoteWindow

StartingPoint:

On Key

Let sMaxSpeed = 40
Let sCoupleSpeed = 4

Drive $Train($Train)

Call TurnTable
Call QuickKeys
Call SpeedSwitching $Train $Car $Speed
Call DropKick $Train $Car $Speed
Call PhastPhunctions
Call o2o
Call jTimer

EndDrive

GoTo StartingPoint
